{
  "page": "Gulltown Girl",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <i><b>Gulltown Girl</b></i> is a trade ship named after <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gulltown_Girl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gulltown_Girl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Podrick_Payne\" title=\"Podrick Payne\">Podrick Payne</a> attempt to book passage on the <i>Gulltown Girl</i> at <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a>. They are refused because the master of the ship believes Brienne to be a <a href=\"/index.php/Whore\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Whore\">whore</a> and he claims his ship is no bawdy house.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gulltown_Girl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 25\">Chapter 25</a>, Brienne V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404182054\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.021 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.042 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 95/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8563/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 420/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 525/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.52 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   37.663      1 -total\n 79.60%   29.979      1 Template:Italic_title\n 16.15%    6.084      1 Template:Ref\n 10.23%    3.854      1 Template:Ref/core\n  3.66%    1.377      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5554-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404182054 and revision id 219026\n -->\n",
